<l><pb facs="154"/><lb n="8" />kaṭalkuṟai paṭuttanīr kalkuṟai paṭaveṟin</l>
<l>tuṭalē ṟurumiṉa mārppa malaimālaimār</l>
<l>muṟṟupu muṟṟupu veyti mutirmukil</l>
<l>poruti<pb facs="155"/><lb n="1" />kal pulipōḻnta pūnuta le<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>lyāṉaik</l>
<l>kurutikkōṭ ṭaḷikaṟai teḷipeṟak kaḻīiyiṉṟu -</l>
<l>kālaik kaṭalpaṭintu kāykatirōṉ pōyavaḻi</l>
<l>mālai <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>laimaṇantu maṇṭuyiṉṟa<lb n="2" /> kaṅkulāṉ</l>
<l>vāṉāṟṟu maḻaitalaii maraṉāṟṟu malarnāṟṟan</l>
<l>tēṉāṟṟu maṇanāṟṟañ ceṟuveyi luṟukālai</l>
<l>kāṉāṟṟuṅ kārnāṟṟaṅ komputirnta kaḷināṟṟan</l>
<l>tāṉāṟṟaṅ ka<space quantity="7" unit="character"/>lantuṭaṉ ṟaḻī<lb n="3" />ivantu tarūumvaiyai -</l>
<l>taṉṉāṟṟa mītu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ṭam<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/><g ref="#ra_r_kal"/>ḻi ṟāṉyāṟṟu</l>
<l>vennāṟṟu vēcaṉai nāṟṟaṅ kutukutuppa</l> 
<l>vūrūr pa<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>yoli koṇṭaṉ ṟuyarmatili</l>
<l>ṉarūr <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>raṇṭēr<lb n="4" />p puravi vaṅ‡m pūṭṭavum</l>
<l>vaṅkap pāṇṭiyiṟ ṟaṇṭē rūravum</l>
<l>vayamāp paṇṇunar matamāp paṇṇavuṅ</l> 
<l>kayamāp pēṇi kalavā tūravu</l>
<l>makaḷir kō<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>mantar puṉai<lb n="5" />yavu</l>
<l>maintar taṇṭār makaḷir <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/></l>
<l>muntuṟal viruppeṟaṭu muṟaimaṟan taṇintava</l>
<l>rāṭuvār poyta laṇivaṇ ṭimirmaṇaṟ</l>
<l>kōṭē reruttat tirumpuṉa liṟku<lb n="6" />ṟuti</l>
<l>māṭa maṟukiṉ maru<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>vi maṟukuṟak</l>
<l>kūṭal viḻaiyun takaittut takaivaiyai -</l>
<l>pukaivakai taiiviṉār pūṅkōtai nallār</l>
<l>takaivakai taiiyiṉār</l>
<l>mā<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> mikami<lb n="7" /><gap reason="lost" quantity="11" unit="character"/>ya</l>
<l>cūṭuṅ kaṇṇiyu mōṭṭu valai<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>yamu</l>
<l>miyalaṇi ya<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>pa vēṟiyama rarippi</l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>ya laṇinōkki yāṅkāṅku varupava</l>
<l><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>rīivaḷai yāramō ṭīttā ṉuṭaṉāka<lb n="8" />k</l> 
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/>vaṇ mēṉiyi<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>ṭu</l>
<l>nontavaṇ māṟṟā ḷivaḷeṉa nōkkat</l> 
<l>tanta kaḷvaṉ camaḻppu mukaṅkāṇmiṉ -</l> 
<l>vāḷi cerucceyta cīṟṟat tavaiyavai<pb facs="156"/><lb n="1" /><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/>ttoyyap pōvā ṇilaikāṇmiṉ -</l> 
<l>eṉavāṅku -</l>
<l>oyyappō vāḷai yuṟaḻntōḷiv vāṇutal</l>
<l>vaiyai maṭuttāṟ kaṭaleṉat te<lb n="2" /><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/> callacce lēṟṟac</l>
<l>ce<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>raippe<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> valluṟa<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> piyātu toṭarpeṉṉa</l>
<l>maṟaliṉāṇ māṟṟāṇ makaḷ</l>
<l>vāyvāḷā niṉṟāḷ</l>
<l>ceṟinakai ci<lb n="3" /><gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>t torutti yavaḷai <gap reason="illegible" quantity="6" unit="character"/></l>
<l>māyappoy kūṭṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>yakki vilaikkaṇikai</l>
<l>peṇmaip potumaip piṇaiyili yaimpulattait</l> 
<l>tuṟṟuva tuṟṟun tuṇaiyitaḻ vā<lb n="4" />yttoṭṭi</l>
<l>muṟṟā naṟunaṟā <g ref="#kompu"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="7" unit="character"/>ṭṭik</l>
<l>kārikai nīrēr vayaṟ kaḷirmak kaḷināñciṉ</l>
<l>mūri tavira muṭukku mutucāṭi</l>
<l>maṭamata ruṇkaṇ kayiṟāka <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>ttut</l>
<l><lb n="5" />taṭameṉṟōṭ ṭoṭṭut tatai<gap reason="illegible" quantity="7" unit="character"/>maṭa viralā</l>
<l>liṭṭārk kiyāḻārttum pāṇiyi lemmiḻaiyait</l> 
<l>toṭṭārttu miṉpat tuṟai<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> tuvi<lb n="6" />keṭṭakaip</l> 
<l>poytaṉ makaḷirkaṇ kāṇa vikuttantiv</l>
<l>vaiyait toḻuvattut tantu vaṭittiṭittu</l>
<l>mattikai mālaiyā mōki yavaittut</l>
<l>toṭarntem<lb n="7" /> merutu toḻilceyyā tō</l> 
<l>viṭuṅkaṭaṉ vēḷāḷark kiṉṟu paṭarntiyān</l>
<l>taṉmārpat taṇṭan tarumārat tāṇmārpu</l>
<l>niṉmārpu mōrotta nīrmaiyako le<lb n="8" />ṉṉāmuṉ</l>
<l>tēṭiṉā rēcac cilamakaḷir maṟṟataṟ</l>
<l>kūṭiṉār vaiyai yakattu [-]</l>
<l>cintikkat tīrum piṇiyāṭ ceṟēṟka</l> 
<l>maintuṟṟāy veñcoṉ<pb facs="157"/><lb n="1" /> maṭamayiṟ cāyalai</l>
<l>vantikka vāreṉa maṉaṟakka <gap reason="illegible" quantity="6" unit="character"/></l>
<l>vēṟṟārai yēṟṟār toḻuta liḷivaravu</l>
<l>pōṟṟāykā ṇaṉṉai puraiyōy puraiyiṉṟu</l>
<l>māṟṟāḷai māṟṟāḷ varavu -</l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="11" unit="character"/> ṉa<lb n="2" />llavai kāṇāmaṟ</l>
<l>ṟantu muḻaviṉ varuvāynīya vāyvāḷā</l>
<l>ventaiyeṉak kītta viṭuvaḷai yārappūṇ</l>
<l>vantavaḻi niṉpāṉ māyak kaḷavaṉṟēṟ</l>
<l>ṟantāṉait tantē tarukku -</l>
<l>mālai yaṇiya vi<lb n="3" />laitantāṉ mātarniṉ</l> 
<l>kāla cilampuṅ kaḻaṟṟuvāṉ cōlai</l>
<l>yatiralaṅ kaṇṇinī yaṉpaṉeṟ kaṟpaṉ</l>
<l>katuvā yavaṉkaḷvaṉ kaḷviṉā ṉallēṉ -</l> 
<l>eṉavāṅku -</l>
<l>vacciya māṉē maṟali<lb n="4" />ṉai māṟṟumakku</l>
<l>nacciṉā ripavai nāṭaṟiya nummavē</l>
<l>cēkkai yiṉiyārpāṟ celvāṉ māṉaiyāḷāṟ</l>
<l>kā kaṭintoḻukal kūṭumō kūṭā</l>
<l>takavuṭai maṅkaiyar<lb n="5" /><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>ṉṟāṇmai cāṉṟā</l>
<l>rikaḻiṉuṅ kēḷvarai yētti yiṟaiñcuvāri</l>
<l>ṉikaḻva taṟiyātu nilluni ṉallāy</l>
<l>makaḷirai maintuṟṟu mārpuṟṟa mainta</l> 
<l>rakalaṅ kaṭiku<g ref="#kompu"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/>ṉ<lb n="6" />pavai yārkkāṉu</l>
<l>muṭiporu ḷaṉṟu muṉiyaṉ muṉiyal</l>
<l>kaṭavarai niṟkumō kāmaṅ koṭiyiyalāy -</l> 
<l>eṉavāṅku -</l>
<l>iṉṉa tuṉiyum pulaviyu mēṟpikkun</l>
<l>teṉ<lb n="7" />ṉavaṉ vaiyaic <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ṟappu -</l>
<l>ko<gap reason="illegible" quantity="8" unit="character"/>pōṟ kuvinta mu<g rend="vowel-sign">ai</g><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/></l>
<l>aravuṭaṉ ṟavaipōl virinta kulai -</l> 
<l>cūṭaivirin tavaipōlak kōlu malar</l>
<l>cuṉaikaḻi<lb n="8" />ntu tū<gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/>riṉ malar -</l>
<l>ci<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>rin tutirntavīyē pu<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>ri yōtoṭu</l>
<l>maruvi corinta tiraiyiṟ ṟurantu</l>
<l>neṭumāl curuṅkai naṭuvaḻip pōntu</l>
<l><pb facs="158"/><lb n="1" /><gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="character"/> ka<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="11" unit="character"/></l>
<l>neṭunīr malipuṉa ṉīṇmāṭak kū<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/></l> 
<l>kaṭimatil peyyum poḻutu -</l>
<l>nāmama rūṭalu naṭpun taṇa<gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/></l>
<l>kāmamuṅ kaḷḷuṅ kalantuṭaṉ pā<lb n="2" />rāṭṭi<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>mamar kātalō ṭāṭap puṇarvittal</l>
<p xml:id="Pari20-intro">pūmali vaiyaik kiyalpu – eṉpatu – paruvavaraviṉkaṭ talaimakaḷa tāṟṟāmai kaṇṭu tūtuviṭac ceṉṟa pāṇaṉ ṟalaimakaṟkuk kārpparuvam vaiyai narviḻavaṇiyuṅ kūṟiyatu – āciriya nalantuvaṉār pāṭṭu – nallaccutaṉā ricai – paṇ kāntāram</p>
         
